text.tspan: Represents one property - that is, one
column of the table. The values in this
column can be accessed with an index.
Each column is a PropertyModel, that can be
accessed with the property ID (column name).
Represents a property table with rows and columns.
Each row is a MetadataEntityModel, that can
be accessed with the row index.
Represents one metadata entity - that is,
one row of the table. The values in this
entity can be accessed with a property ID.
